title: Curse of the Weird
description:
Issues 1-4 of 'Curse of the Weird'

Marvel Comics, 1993, 32 page each

Written and Illustrated by Stan Lee, Steve Ditko, Bill Everett, Russ Heath Jr, Dick Briefer, Carl Wessler, Joe Orlando, Basil Wolverton, Paul Becton, Jack Davis, Ashley Posella, Art Simek

An anthology reprinting stories from some of the masters of the medium that originally appeared in various publications in the late 40s and early 50s.
